name: CrownTown☀️
description: Goal: It's a trap!. Our trait: Chuck Norris can divide by zero.

name: Nova l Hispania
description: Goal: The Shield is down! Commence attack on the Death star's main reactor. Our trait: Chuck Norris doesn't need a java compiler, he goes straight to .war.

name: 硬中华
description: Goal: I've got a bad feeling about this. Our trait: Chuck Norris can compile syntax errors.

name: Rocket's
description: Goal: You can run, but you'll only die tired. Our trait: Chuck Norris can spawn threads that complete before they are started.

name: QLASH Eclipse
description: Goal: R2-D2, you know better than to trust a strange computer. Our trait: When Chuck Norris' code fails to compile the compiler apologises.

name: KingZ Rush
description: Goal: We're doomed. Our trait: Chuck Norris' keyboard doesn't have a F1 key, the computer asks him for help.

name: Always Baked
description: Goal: Twice the pride, double the fall. Our trait: When Chuck Norris presses Ctrl+Alt+Delete, worldwide computer restart is initiated.

name: NoA
description: Goal: I find your lack of faith disturbing. Our trait: Chuck Norris doesn't get compiler errors.

name: darkzero
description: Goal: You are unwise to lower your defenses. Our trait: Chuck Norris's first program was kill -9.

name: Spacestation
description: Goal: There is a great disturbance in the Force. Our trait: Chuck Norris can solve the Towers of Hanoi in one move.

name: Team Legacy
description: Goal: Let the hate flow through you. Our trait: Chuck Norris can unit test an entire application with a single assert.

name: AK Syndicate
description: Goal: Never tell me the odds. Our trait: Chuck Norris doesn't need a debugger, he just stares down the bug until the code confesses.

name: UNAUFHALTSAM
description: Goal: Solo, la pa loiya Solo. Our trait: Chuck Norris can access private methods.

name: QLASH Sentry
description: Goal: You'll find I'm full of surprises. Our trait: Chuck Norris can instantiate an abstract class.

name: Nova I Aryayi
description: Goal: Your overconfidence is your weakness. Our trait: Chuck Norris doesn't need to know about class factory pattern. He can instantiate interfaces.

name: Nice Strategy
description: Goal: The Force will be with you. Always. Our trait: For Chuck Norris, NP-Hard = O(1).

name: Undiscovered™
description: Goal: Remember your focus determines your reality. Our trait: Chuck Norris knows the last digit of PI.

name: Outcasts™️
description: Goal: Wars not make one great. Our trait: No statement can catch the ChuckNorrisException.

name: Team Solid
description: Goal: A Jedi uses the Force for knowledge and defense, never for attack. Our trait: Chuck Norris went out of an infinite loop.

name: vikings br
description: Goal: Do. Or do not. There is no try. Our trait: Chuck Norris can access the DB from the UI.
